# Keep the Docker build context small. The firmware build needs: Cargo.toml/lock,
# rust-toolchain.toml, build.rs, .cargo/, src/, assets/. Everything below is build output,
# VCS, editor state, or docs — none of it is needed to compile the firmware.
target/
.git/
.cachebro/
.claude/
.cursor/
.vscode/
docs/
specs/
.github/
scripts/
*.md
